{"tid":1076847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《35公尺恐怖平交道》92歲老人被撞死惹議 年輕網友也直呼超扯不敢走……","createTime":"2019-03-25T07:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T14:32:26.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef57e4c65553c711a817ea161a171a45a67259f","tid":1076847,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKGaqaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKGaqaQ.jpg&h=3146ef5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本神奈川縣逗子市這個星期發生一位92歲男性被電車撞死的事件，事發的平交道因此成為話題，因為這個平交道不但長達35公尺而且竟然連個信號都沒有，也就是說必需時時查看左右來車連續走過9條線路，別說是92歲的老人了，網友直呼就算是年輕人也不敢走啊！而這種恐怖平交道至今依然存在的原因也引發議論，是不是因為當地居民會抗議所以難以撤除呢？難道沒有其他改善的方法嗎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n92歲老人遭電車撞上身亡！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKGaqaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKGaqaU.jpg&h=b50ce1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3月21日，日本神奈川縣逗子市的逗子車站附近有一位橫越平交道的92歲老人遭撞身亡，而這個平交道的全貌被報導出來以後立刻引發議論&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n長達35公尺，沒有半個信號！？<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKGaqaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKGaqaY.jpg&h=e2a3f4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個平交道需要橫越35公尺，一共9條線路，而且竟然完全沒有信號管制，因此必需隨時注意左右來車！日本警方在現場發現耳機和收音機，因此懷疑那位92歲老人當時正在聽廣播才會沒發現電車接近，從Google街景來看&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKGaqac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKGaqac.jpg&h=f6aebb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發生意外的平交道<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKGaqac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKGaqac.jpg&h=f6aebb5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b906bff5ddbfa6424cad6a18a52cd487ee42946","tid":1076847,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"天堂直通車"},{"pid":"fb2e7d2a2602056b06d074b212ae7259b9aa6360","tid":1076847,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"衛星空拍圖可以看出這條路要穿越密密麻麻的鐵軌！<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKaXrKQ.jpg[/日本網友們議論紛紛為什麼至今還有這種恐怖的平交道，而且很多人都說自己也沒信心能夠走過去，更別說是92歲的老人了&hellip;&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F74%2F15%2FqJeWoKCWmKaXrKQ.jpg%5B%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%80%91%E8%AD%B0%E8%AB%96%E7%B4%9B%E7%B4%9B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E9%80%99%E7%A8%AE%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E4%BA%A4%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A0%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%88%A5%E8%AA%AA%E6%98%AF92%E6%AD%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6fdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=0b1a07e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/74/15/qJeWoKCWmKaXrKQ.jpg[/日本網友們議論紛紛為什麼至今還有這種恐怖的平交道，而且很多人都說自己也沒信心能夠走過去，更別說是92歲的老人了&hellip;&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n「這就算是健康的人要通過也很誇張吧？」<br />\n「沒警報也沒遮斷器的35公尺，年輕人也會覺得恐怖吧」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民眾抗議才無法撤除這麼危險的平交道，畢竟如果封了這條路，就必需多走260公尺遠才能繞過線路！而且就算架了天橋，92歲要爬上去可能也不容易啊&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"db595f91d63c7f2b420f89bce587ebb4aa02a6a8","tid":1076847,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2e7d2a2602056b06d074b212ae7259b9aa6360","tid":1076847,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"衛星空拍圖可以看出這條路要穿越密密麻麻的鐵軌！<br />\n[img]<a href